---
title: Carb Smart Tomato-Caper Pork Chops with Parm Roasted Veggies
description: Capers make this tomato sauce shine by lending a lovely subtle brininess to these pork chops. Golden roasted veggies sprinkled with Parmesan goodness round out this light and satisfying plate!

